snippet.title: Johnny Depp Finally Talks Amber Heard: "She's Good For Me"
snippet.description:
You'd think Johnny Depp is promoting his wedding, but in fact, he's in the middle of a media tour for his April 17 release, Transcendence. Nonetheless, Johnny gushed about his bride-to-be, Amber Heard — and his diamond engagement ring! — twice in the last two days, and we are breaking down the latest with entertainment correspondent Lyndsey Rodrigues.
